<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1986] Batch Gets</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1986</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Put as well as Delete allow batch operations using HTable.put(List) and HTable.delete(ArrayList).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We often need to fetch a few thousand rows per id and currently have to issue an RPC call (using HTable.get(Get)) for each of the rows. Support for batch gets, a la HTable.get(List) could easily improve performance since only one RPC call per region server must be issued.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
